00:17:33,768 --> 00:17:37,035
And I took a bath last night, so...

317
00:17:37,035 --> 00:17:38,468
Really?

318
00:17:38,468 --> 00:17:42,168
But...

319
00:17:42,168 --> 00:17:45,368
