00:18:49,768 --> 00:18:54,468
And Mr. Banba kept emphasizing the fact that he used to be a bookworm.

344
00:18:54,468 --> 00:18:56,668
Is that all?

345
00:18:56,668 --> 00:18:58,268
Yes.

346
00:18:58,268 --> 00:19:01,468
Would you like to go ask the lady now?

347
00:19:01,468 --> 00:19:03,468
But...

348
00:19:03,468 --> 00:19:05,768
I can't help feeling that the lady

349
00:19:05,768 --> 00:19:10,368
already knows who the man of her memories is.

350
00:19:12,268 --> 00:19:17,135
I've seen these in dramas and on movies, but...

351
00:19:17,135 --> 00:19:18,768
I sure am surprised

352
00:19:18,768 --> 00:19:21,139
to find that there is actually a gorgeous bath like this.

353
00:19:24,168 --> 00:19:26,268
Hey there, Mr. Detective.

